headline: Kenvue Announces Participation in the Morgan Stanley Global Consumer & Retail Conference
summary: SKILLMAN, N.J., November 25, 2024--Kenvue Inc. (NYSE: KVUE) ("Kenvue") today announced the Company’s participation in the Morgan Stanley Global Consumer & Retail Conference in New York City. Thibaut Mongon, Chief Executive Officer and Paul Ruh, Chief Financial Officer will participate in a fireside chat on Wednesday, December 4, 2024, at 11:45 a.m. Eastern Time.
